{
  "stem": "11844.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I-- I cannot kill people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not my job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then he said to me, well, who else can?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have her confidence.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know who she is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're convinced.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She died shortly thereafter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What else?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] [INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the meantime, I got more and more involved in all of that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was in Holland a camp by the name of Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Westerbork was not a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Westerbork was a camp where all the people in-- the Jews-- in Holland who were arrested or had to come, they all came to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they stayed there for weeks or months, depending on many circumstances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And every Tuesday-- every Tuesday-- a train, which was called the 'transport trein,' left from Westerbork to Auschwitz or to Sobibor with about 1,000 people in it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Holland had 130,000 Jews when the Nazi came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About 104,000 were deported in those two camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And maybe several hundred, maybe as many as 1,000, came back out of the 130,000 Jews living in Holland and that were deported.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For practical purposes-- no practical purposes-- nobody came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the 30,000 Jews which still were in Holland after the war, there was 20,000 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] underground people who survived, and 10, maybe, mixed marriages or special circumstances.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, those are approximate numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had a way of getting boys-- not girls-- out of Westerbork and put them into the Organization Todt de France.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was done through an underground tunnel where people were at work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And some people that dug-- Hanneman was the name of the guy who did it-- they-- they did a-- a little tunnel underground.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
